synopsis.value: TEST DIALOGUE: Pavery Glosty used to be an alderman/civil servant in Baldurs Gate Lower City, until he was muscled out of his position by followers of the Absolute, who used their influence to replace him with one of their own. Since then, hes gone off the rails on a bender. If you manage to find him and sober him up/talk with him on his level, youll gain some useful information you can turn against some of the Absolutes agents in the city.
